snippet.textDisplay:
I have to admit, the tactile feedback from playing Vinyl records is much more intimate and satisfying. I think something is lost when digital components are introduced by the DJs. Much like holding a book, touching the pages and the smell of pages, it creates a more profound experience. In the room's lighting , you can almost see Evan Green sitting cross-legged on the couch, smoking a cigarette and looking sexy whilst sipping from some fine wine.

Great selection of tracks!
-G
